---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Skills | Julian Molina-Goni">
  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 sm:py-16">
    <header class="mb-10 sm:mb-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-3">
        Skills & Tech Stack
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        I design, build, and operate cloud-native systems, automation workflows, and production applications. These are the tools and technologies I work with most day-to-day. Everything below is real text (not images), so it's fully searchable, accessible, and easy to scan.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Core Technologies -->
    <section class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">
        Core Technologies
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4 text-center">
        My primary technology stack for cloud engineering and full-stack development.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white font-medium">AWS</span>
        <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white font-medium">Python</span>
        <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white font-medium">Docker</span>
        <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white font-medium">ECS</span>
        <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white font-medium">React</span>
        <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white font-medium">Lambda</span>
        <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white font-medium">CloudFormation</span>
        <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white font-medium">REST APIs</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-10 sm:space-y-12">
      <!-- Cloud & DevOps -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">
          Cloud & DevOps
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Designing and operating AWS infrastructure with a focus on reliability, cost optimization, and automation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="skill-chip">Application Load Balancer (ALB)</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">AWS</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">AWS Systems Manager</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Bedrock</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">CloudFormation</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">CloudTrail</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">CloudWatch</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Docker</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">EC2</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">ECR</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">ECS</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">EKS</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">EventBridge</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">IAM</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Infrastructure as Code (IaC)</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Kubernetes</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Lambda</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Lightsail</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Network Load Balancer (NLB)</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">RDS</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">S3</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Serverless Architectures</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Textract</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Programming & Scripting -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">
          Programming & Scripting
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Languages and scripting tools I use to automate infrastructure, build services, and create internal tools.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="skill-chip">Bash</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">C#</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">C++</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Go</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Node.js</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">PowerShell</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Python</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">TypeScript</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- APIs & Integrations -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">
          APIs & Integrations
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Building and integrating REST APIs, webhooks, and third-party platforms—especially in communication, healthcare, and data-heavy environments. I specialize in wiring systems together—telephony, CRMs, EHRs, dashboards, and internal tools—via robust, well-tested API integrations.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="skill-chip">8x8 API</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Error Handling & Retry / Backoff</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Gmail API</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">JSON / HTTP / Pagination</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">NHL Stats API</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">NICE inContact API</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">OAuth2 & API Authentication</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">REST API Design</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">REST API Integration</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">RingCentral API</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Webhook Workflows</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">WordPress REST API</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Frameworks & Libraries -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">
          Frameworks & Libraries
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Frontend and backend frameworks I use to build dashboards, APIs, and full-stack applications.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="skill-chip">Astro</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">FastAPI</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Material Design</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Node.js (Express)</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">React</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">React PWA</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Ruby on Rails</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">TailwindCSS</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Databases & Storage -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">
          Databases & Storage
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Working with relational and NoSQL databases to support event-driven systems and data-heavy workloads.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="skill-chip">DynamoDB</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Microsoft SQL Server</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">MySQL</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">PostgreSQL</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">S3 (Object Storage)</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">SQLite</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CI/CD, Observability & Automation -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">
          CI/CD, Observability & Automation
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Tooling that keeps deployments reliable, traceable, and fast—from commit to production.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="skill-chip">Alerting & Incident Response</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">AWS CodePipeline</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Blue/Green Deployments</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Centralized Logging</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">CloudWatch Logs & Metrics</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Cost Optimization Automation</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">GitHub Actions</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">GitLab CI/CD</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Systems, Platforms & IT -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">
          Systems, Platforms & IT Operations
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">
          A decade of experience in systems engineering, IT management, and endpoint operations in regulated environments.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="skill-chip">Active Directory</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Endpoint Management</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">HIPAA / HITRUST / PCI Context</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Linux</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">macOS</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Patch Management</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">SaaS Management</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">SSO & Identity</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">VPN & Remote Access</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Windows</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Tools & Platforms -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">
          Tools & Platforms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Supporting tools that help ship, monitor, and maintain production systems and internal platforms.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="skill-chip">Cloudflare</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Confluence / Documentation</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Dynadot</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Flywheel</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Git</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">GitHub</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">GitLab</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Jira</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Mailchimp</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Namecheap</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Netlify</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">OBS / FFmpeg (Streaming & Recording)</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">OCR Processing</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">TreeMap Visualization</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">WordPress</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Certifications -->
      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-4">
          Certifications
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white">AWS SysOps Administrator (2025)</span>
          <span class="skill-chip bg-blue-600 border-blue-500 text-white">AWS Cloud Practitioner (2020, Renewed 2023)</span>
          <span class="skill-chip bg-red-600 border-red-500 text-white">CompTIA A+ (2020, Renewed 2023)</span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .skill-chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background-color: #374151;
    color: #f3f4f6;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #4b5563;
  }

  .skill-chip:hover {
    background-color: #4b5563;
    color: white;
    border-color: #6b7280;
  }
</style>